		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, most games have 8KB of SRAM. However there are some that has 1KB or 16k, even 32k of RAM that could be battery backed. For just about every game you need a 8K save. Just name it RomName.sav and it'll be fine. Just remember you'll have to power off/reset so it can write the save to the card.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


